# Copy to `.env` and fill in. `.env` is gitignored.
#
# Clerk publishable key — drives the sign-in wizard. A `pk_test_*` key is
# public by design (it identifies the Clerk frontend instance; it grants
# no privileged access), so the development default below is safe to
# share. NEVER put a `pk_live_*` key or any secret key here — secret keys
# belong in the OS keychain / vault, never in a build-time env file.
VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_YW1hemVkLWNvZC02Ny5jbGVyay5hY2NvdW50cy5kZXYk
